How to Download and Install Power BI Desktop (Step by Step)
Step 1: Open the Official Microsoft Website
Go to the official Power BI Desktop download page:
Microsoft Power BI Desktop Download
Microsoft provides Power BI Desktop free of cost. 
________________________________________
Step 2: Click on Download
•	Click the Download button. 
•	Select PBIDesktopSetup_x64.exe (64-bit) (Recommended). 
•	Click Next to start downloading. 
________________________________________
Step 3: Open the Downloaded File
After the download is complete:
•	Go to your Downloads folder. 
•	Double-click PBIDesktopSetup_x64.exe. 
________________________________________
Step 4: Start the Installation
The setup wizard will open.
1.	Click Next. 
2.	Accept the License Agreement. 
3.	Click Next. 
4.	Choose the installation location (or keep the default). 
5.	Click Install. 
________________________________________
Step 5: Wait for Installation
The installation usually takes 2–5 minutes, depending on your computer.
________________________________________
Step 6: Finish Installation
•	Click Finish. 
•	Open Power BI Desktop from the Start Menu or Desktop. 
________________________________________
Step 7: Sign In (Optional)
You can:
•	Click Sign In using your Microsoft account, or 
•	Click Skip if you only want to practice locally.
